## 🏗️ ARCHITECTURE RULES

### ❌ NEVER:
- Make API calls directly from screens/components
- Put business logic in UI components
- Mutate data outside the services layer
- Use `fetch()` directly in screens

### ✅ ALWAYS:
- Follow data flow: `UI → services/ → API → backend`
- Import and use service functions: `import { fetchGroups } from '../../services/groups.service'`
- Keep screens thin (UI composition only)
- Put ALL API calls in `services/` directory
- Put business logic in services (frontend) or services (backend)

### Example:
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT
import { createGroup } from '../../services/groups.service';

function MyScreen() {
  const handleCreate = async () => {
    await createGroup(data);
  };
}

// ❌ WRONG
function MyScreen() {
  const handleCreate = async () => {
    await fetch('/api/groups', { method: 'POST', body: data });
  };
}
```

